51
00:03:51,089 --> 00:03:52,797
I wanna know more about this guy you like!

52
00:03:52,853 --> 00:03:56,104
Hmm. I wouldn't say that I like him, not yet anyway.

53
00:03:56,159 --> 00:03:58,550
