55
00:04:01,631 --> 00:04:02,228
Ahh.

56
00:04:02,252 --> 00:04:03,364
It's that guy.

57
00:04:03,984 --> 00:04:06,038
Oh, so you know who I'm talking about, then?

58
00:04:06,109 --> 00:04:07,645
