Don't worry about me!

131
00:07:24,300 --> 00:07:25,925
I'm surprised to see you here, that's all!

132
00:07:26,042 --> 00:07:28,554
Oh! Could you be out shopping today, too, Ms. Sakurai?

133
00:07:28,681 --> 00:07:30,943
Yes! There's a great sale on green onions today,

134
00:07:30,968 --> 00:07:32,597
so I figured I'd go out and pick some up.

135
00:07:32,859 --> 00:07:33,957
Green onions, huh?

136
00:07:34,264 --> 00:07:38,513
Well, if you ever find yourself needing bamboo
sprouts, just give me a shout and I'll get you some!

137
00:07:38,582 --> 00:07:40,908
Uh, you have extra bamboo sprouts?

138
00:07:41,025 --> 00:07:42,109
