145
00:07:57,186 --> 00:07:59,769
This wasn't some chance encounter. It was destiny.

146
00:08:00,460 --> 00:08:02,668
I never believed in this kind of stuff before,

147
00:08:03,320 --> 00:08:04,677
but I think I get it now.

148
