...maybe we should sit down.

152
00:08:14,536 --> 00:08:15,317
Don't worry about me!

153
00:08:15,359 --> 00:08:17,406
I'm doing completely fine, 100 percent fine!

154
00:08:17,484 --> 00:08:19,692
I wouldn't want you to trouble
yourself with something like...

155
00:08:19,775 --> 00:08:21,251
...maybe we should sit down.

156
00:08:21,584 --> 00:08:22,771
With something like...

