00:08:22,873 --> 00:08:24,415
...maybe we should sit down.

158
00:08:25,203 --> 00:08:26,863
...maybe we should sit down.

159
00:08:28,688 --> 00:08:30,317
...maybe we should sit down.

160
00:08:33,237 --> 00:08:34,390
This is the best.

161
00:08:34,415 --> 00:08:35,757
I hope it never ends.

162
00:08:35,871 --> 00:08:38,331
I know! I have a great idea, Ms. Sakurai!

163
00:08:38,402 --> 00:08:41,334
There's a park a few blocks down, so
why don't we go down there and sit down?

164
00:08:41,359 --> 00:08:42,454
Uh, okay!

165
00:08:45,002 --> 00:08:46,291
Oh, man.

166
00:08:46,439 --> 00:08:49,035
I can't believe this is actually happening right now.

167
00:08:49,701 --> 00:08:51,378
Hang on!

168
00:08:51,585 --> 00:08:53,804
Could this be... considered a date?!

169
00:08:57,528 --> 00:08:59,018
Why is she here?

170
00:08:59,292 --> 00:09:01,375
Actually, you know what? I'm fine!

171
00:09:01,400 --> 00:09:03,109
So maybe we should just turn around.

172
00:09:03,165 --> 00:09:04,605
A student, here? Now?

173
00:09:04,744 --> 00:09:06,342
I can't have her seeing us together.

174
00:09:07,309 --> 00:09:09,619
Uh... Hey! What are you two doing over there?

175
00:09:09,881 --> 00:09:10,889
D-Don't be silly!

176
00:09:10,914 --> 00:09:13,000
This is just a completely casual meeting between adults.

177
00:09:13,025 --> 00:09:13,837
And, uh, that's it!

178
00:09:13,900 --> 00:09:15,077
Fancy seeing you here!

179
00:09:15,118 --> 00:09:16,584
If I didn't know any better,

180
00:09:16,609 --> 00:09:19,065
I'd say you two were on a secret date or something.

181
00:09:19,132 --> 00:09:21,674
