Well, it's been a lovely coincidence
seeing you here, Ms. Sakurai!

207
00:10:21,995 --> 00:10:23,874
And wouldn't ya know it, there's a student here, too!

208
00:10:23,899 --> 00:10:26,859
What are the chances of seeing two people
from the school in the exact same place!

209
00:10:26,949 --> 00:10:28,157
Hm? What was your name?

210
00:10:28,220 --> 00:10:29,682
It's Aioi, isn't that right?

211
00:10:29,734 --> 00:10:31,464
Just kidding! Of course I'd remember!

212
00:10:31,650 --> 00:10:32,350
Uh...

213
00:10:32,375 --> 00:10:33,458
Well! In any case!

214
00:10:33,621 --> 00:10:38,222
I've got places to go and people to see, so if
you'll excuse me, I'm gonna hit the 'ol dusty trail!

215
00:10:48,895 --> 00:10:53,259
Maybe... I should pick up some green onions.

216
00:10:57,109 --> 00:10:59,109
Sorry for calling you out like this.

217
00:10:59,852 --> 00:11:01,281
You sleep okay last night?

218
00:11:01,473 --> 00:11:05,203
I did, but... I had the most peculiar dream.

219
00:11:05,631 --> 00:11:07,515
Oh, really? What happened?

220
00:11:07,770 --> 00:11:11,283
Well, um... we were standing here kissing.

221
00:11:12,165 --> 00:11:14,467
What if I made that dream a reality?

222
00:11:15,234 --> 00:11:17,275
Hey! Uh, Hakase!

223
00:11:17,352 --> 00:11:18,969
Let's go get you some more snacks!

224
00:11:19,117 --> 00:11:21,784
