225
00:11:22,001 --> 00:11:23,929
Save your questions for after.

226
00:11:23,956 --> 00:11:26,831
Oh, my! Sir!

227
00:11:39,383 --> 00:11:41,403
After one whole month of investigating,

228
00:11:41,428 --> 00:11:46,234
I've determined that Nano Shinonome visits
the supermarket in this district every Saturday.

229
00:11:46,270 --> 00:11:49,144
If my calculations are correct, she'll be arriving soon.

230
00:11:49,195 --> 00:11:51,779
And once she does, I'll be right behind her.

231
00:11:51,881 --> 00:11:53,292
When I find my opening,

232
00:11:53,317 --> 00:11:58,192
I'll call upon my trusty friend, Mr. Short
Circuit, once again to assist me in this abduction.

233
00:11:58,217 --> 00:11:59,251
For science!

234
00:11:59,451 --> 00:12:00,857
It's the perfect plan!

235
00:12:00,985 --> 00:12:04,132
Today shall be the day I study you, Miss Shinonome!

236
00:12:07,568 --> 00:12:08,408
Or not!

237
00:12:08,478 --> 00:12:09,895
Why isn't she showing up?

238
00:12:09,985 --> 00:12:12,719
Could it be that she doesn't
come to the supermarket every week?

239
00:12:12,763 --> 00:12:14,482
Maybe my calculations were off.

240
00:12:16,386 --> 00:12:18,352
No. I can't give up now.

241
00:12:18,431 --> 00:12:21,287
I've already waited this long,
so I can't let it be for nothing!

242
00:12:21,417 --> 00:12:22,247
Hmm.

243
00:12:22,532 --> 00:12:24,904
I knew it! So it is you, Ms. Nakamura.

244
00:12:25,083 --> 00:12:26,542
Fancy seeing you here.

245
00:12:26,567 --> 00:12:28,974
Likewise, you walking pair of sideburns!

246
00:12:29,069 --> 00:12:30,264
Uh, hello there.

247
00:12:30,353 --> 00:12:33,614
I hardly recognized you without your usual lab coat on.

248
00:12:33,970 --> 00:12:36,956
